- **Categories covered: 17 major semantic domains**
- **Primary sources:**
  - Wiktionary Lombard Swadesh list (comprehensive comparative linguistics database)
  - Centro di dialettologia e di etnografia (CDE) Ticinese dialect publications
  - Alpine Lombard linguistic research
  - Contemporary Western Lombard sources

